&lt;h4 id="layer-2-ai-processing-the-brain"&gt;Layer 2: AI Processing (The Brain)&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;These tools handle the &amp;ldquo;smart&amp;rdquo; parts — understanding text, making decisions, generating content.&lt;/p&gt;
